{"tid":1301213,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"解放軍駐港部隊司令向美國強調 不會出兵干預香港事務","createTime":"2019-07-09T14:49:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-09T16:28:24.000Z","uid":5195,"like":41,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"ee80e66299aba36d5a9ae07e80018bffcb47577e","tid":1301213,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T14:49:11.000Z","msg":"路透社今天報道，指解放軍駐香港部隊司令員陳道祥少將上月曾在香港，會晤美國國防部亞太安全事務首席副助理部長海大衛（David Helvey），具體日期是6月13日，即剛好在6.12警民衝突後。<br />\n<br />\n路透引述消息人士表示，陳道祥在會上表示，解放軍駐香港部隊不會違反一直以來的政策，干預香港事務。<br />\n<br />\n據稱雙方的會面是由陳道祥發出邀請，並在解放軍駐香港部隊大廈內進行。消息人士續指，「這舉動令人意外，因為是由他自行提起。在這個敏感時刻，它是一個清晰的訊號」。<br />\n<br />\n美國國防部一名不願透露姓名官員證實，陳道祥曾與美國國防部一名高官會晤，並提及解放軍駐港部隊不會干預香港的事務，但基於會面屬私人性質，所以拒絕透露更多詳情。"},{"pid":"f9a0926866a92bec506c96372be29acc7643fb81","tid":1301213,"uid":20815,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T14:50:54.000Z","msg":"俾美帝照肺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40d3814f7d73e284df1cb620bd8e086c3d4fb064","tid":1301213,"uid":11001,"like":42,"dislike":0,"score":42,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T14:51:46.000Z","msg":"美帝先係解放軍最高司令 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2034cb156bf3f2102a66cd51973ee639020152a5","tid":1301213,"uid":52230,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T14:52:25.000Z","msg":"笑撚死 淆到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31744b6f604ce2eb54198f0edbe15350db1d3bb6","tid":1301213,"uid":51701,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T14:52:36.000Z","msg":"Sir, you have my word, how about my family in US ? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4badeb236a25a3db8f0bb040ae0605b11284a53b","tid":1301213,"uid":61625,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"31744b6f604ce2eb54198f0edbe15350db1d3bb6","tid":1301213,"uid":51701,"like":24,"dislike":0,"